PrecisApprove the appointment by the Minister of Finance of Michel Caron, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Petro-Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term ending August 28, 1994, in the place of Frederick W. Gorbet.
